					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Back on topic.  I notice when people talk about designing a console, people tend to not like the idea of having multiple graphics modes like the SNES, but honestly, I think it was a good idea at the time because if every BG layer was 4bpp there would only be 2 layers of parallax with it's access speed of 5.37Mhz.  I think a couple modes might need to be changed a bit though, such as making everything packed pixel.</div>

